          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two independent  measurements  of  the  N-15(g,n)N-14",
                " reaction cross section have been made using both  an",
                " enriched-gas  and  ammonium sulphate powder targets.",
                " The results are  self-consistent  (only  gas  target",
                " data  are presented),  but reveal discrepancies with",
                " an  earlier  measurement  of  this  cross   section,",
                " particularly  in the giant dipole resonance  region,",
                " and with a measurement of N-15(g,n-0) cross section.",
                " These  discrepancies  are  discussed  and in general",
                " resolved.  The results are used in conjunction  with",
                " other  isospin-selective  reactions  data on N-15 to",
                " elucidate the isospin distribution of e1  states  in",
                " N-15."
              ]
            }
          ],
